milestones.description: Bas Zuiderent has become the top scorer for NED in ODIs with 371 runs, going past Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk's 322
Bas Zuiderent has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for NED breaking Ryan ten Doeschate's record
Ashish Bagai has scored 4 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for CAN breaking John Davison's record
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (22) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
Jeroen Smits has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for NED, going past Marcel Schewe's 3
This is the lowest match aggregate (401) involving teams Netherlands & Canada in ODIs
